<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>London & Iceland Family Guidebook</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #202124;
      --muted: #6f6b63;
      --cream: #fff8ef;
      --paper: #fffdf8;
      --clay: #c8653b;
      --sky: #80b7c8;
      --moss: #68785f;
      --gold: #e7b75f;
      --ice: #d9edf2;
      --charcoal: #2c3035;
      --line: rgba(32, 33, 36, 0.12);
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(32, 33, 36, 0.12);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(128, 183, 200, 0.25), transparent 34rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 12%, rgba(231, 183, 95, 0.18), transparent 24rem),
        var(--cream);
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      background: rgba(255, 248, 239, 0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .75rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 2.4rem;
      height: 2.4rem;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--charcoal);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(44, 48, 53, .24);
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: .5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: .88rem;
      padding: .65rem .9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .55);
      border: 1px solid rgba(32, 33, 36, .08);
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 78vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.12fr .88fr;
      gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
      align-items: center;
      padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem) clamp(1rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      padding: .5rem .8rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--clay);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(32, 33, 36, .08);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 9vw, 8rem);
      line-height: .88;
      letter-spacing: -.065em;
      max-width: 11ch;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 43rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.4vw, 1.32rem);
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    }

    .hero-card {
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transform: rotate(1.2deg);
    }

    .poster-img {
      min-height: 29rem;
      border-radius: 1.4rem;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(128,183,200,.88), rgba(217,237,242,.7) 38%, rgba(231,183,95,.82) 39%, rgba(231,183,95,.82) 56%, rgba(104,120,95,.82) 57%),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513635269975-59663e0ac1ad?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80');
      background-size: cover;
      background-blend-mode: multiply;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .poster-img::after {
      content: "LONDON → ICELAND";
      position: absolute;
      left: 1.2rem;
      bottom: 1rem;
      color: white;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: .9;
      letter-spacing: -.06em;
      text-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.38);
    }

    .stat-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: .75rem;
      margin-top: .9rem;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 1.1rem;
      background: #f7efe5;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .stat span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: .35rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    section {
      padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem) clamp(1rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 5rem);
      line-height: .94;
      letter-spacing: -.055em;
    }

    .section-head p {
      max-width: 34rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .map-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: .8fr 1.2fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .timeline {
      display: grid;
      gap: .8rem;
    }

    .day-card, .place-card, .stay-card {
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 38px rgba(32,33,36,.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .day-card {
      padding: 1rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 4.5rem 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .date-badge {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      border-radius: 1.2rem;
      color: white;
      background: var(--clay);
      font-weight: 950;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.05;
    }

    .date-badge.blue { background: var(--sky); color: var(--charcoal); }
    .date-badge.green { background: var(--moss); }
    .date-badge.gold { background: var(--gold); color: var(--charcoal); }

    .day-card h3 { margin: .1rem 0 .4rem; }
    .day-card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

    .map-wrap {
      min-height: 36rem;
      border-radius: 1.6rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      background: white;
    }

    .map-wrap iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: 0;
      display: block;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .place-card img, .stay-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 15rem;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      filter: saturate(1.05) contrast(1.02);
    }

    .card-body { padding: 1rem; }

    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: .65rem;
      padding: .35rem .65rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #f2e4d1;
      color: var(--clay);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: .76rem;
      letter-spacing: .02em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .tag.ice { background: var(--ice); color: #276473; }
    .tag.stay { background: #e6eadf; color: var(--moss); }

    .place-card h3, .stay-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 .45rem;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
    }

    .place-card p, .stay-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .mini-note {
      margin-top: .85rem;
      padding-top: .85rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-weight: 850;
      color: var(--ink) !important;
    }

    .stays-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .footer {
      margin: 2rem clamp(1rem, 5vw, 5rem) 3rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 2rem;
      background: var(--charcoal);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer p { margin: 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,.72); }

    @media (max-width: 950px) {
      .hero, .map-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .cards { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .map-wrap { min-height: 28rem; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .topbar { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; }
      nav { justify-content: flex-start; }
      .section-head { display: block; }
      .section-head p { margin-top: 1rem; }
      .cards, .stays-grid, .stat-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-card { transform: none; }
      .poster-img { min-height: 23rem; }
      .day-card { grid-template-columns: 3.8rem 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="brand"><span class="brand-mark">✈</span> London & Iceland</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#itinerary">Itinerary</a>
      <a href="#places">Places</a>
      <a href="#stays">Stays</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">June 3–13, 2026 · Family Guidebook</div>
        <h1>Two cities, one wild little adventure.</h1>
        <p>A vivid, easy-to-use travel guide for our London city days and Iceland road trip. This site will hold the live map, daily plans, must-see places, food stops, waterfalls, campsites, hotels, and all the little notes we do not want to forget.</p>
      </div>
      <aside class="hero-card" aria-label="Trip summary card">
        <div class="poster-img"></div>
        <div class="stat-row">
          <div class="stat"><strong>3</strong><span>London nights</span></div>
          <div class="stat"><strong>7</strong><span>Iceland nights</span></div>
          <div class="stat"><strong>∞</strong><span>Waterfalls</span></div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section id="itinerary">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>Itinerary + Live Map</h2>
        <p>Use this page as the main trip dashboard. The cards can become day-by-day plans once the schedule is finalized, and the map below uses your Google My Maps embed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="map-grid">
        <div class="timeline">
          <article class="day-card">
            <div class="date-badge">Jun<br>3</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Arrive in London</h3>
              <p>Land at Heathrow or Gatwick, check in at Hyatt Regency London Blackfriars, then ease into the trip with nearby food, a walk, and a low-pressure first night.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="day-card">
            <div class="date-badge blue">Jun<br>4–5</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Classic London Days</h3>
              <p>Borough Market, Buckingham Palace, St. Paul’s Cathedral, Tower Bridge, Big Ben, London Eye, British Museum, Sky Garden, Dishoom, and more.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="day-card">
            <div class="date-badge green">Jun<br>6</div>
            <div>
              <h3>London to Iceland</h3>
              <p>Travel day to Iceland. Pick up campervan or rental setup, settle in, and start the Iceland portion of the adventure.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="day-card">
            <div class="date-badge gold">Jun<br>6–13</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Iceland Road Trip</h3>
              <p>Rainbow Street, Sky Lagoon, Blue Lagoon, Geysir, Gullfoss, Thingvellir, Diamond Beach, Jökulsárlón, Dettifoss, Reynisfjara, Skógafoss, and more.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="map-wrap">
          <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1LNLXpkGFz1LaQtOkBwMYtQdJb1voZjA&ehbc=2E312F" loading="lazy"></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="places">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>Places We’re Visiting</h2>
        <p>Each card can include 1–2 photos, what the place is famous for, why it matters, and our personal reason for visiting.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cards">
        <article class="place-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513635269975-59663e0ac1ad?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="London skyline placeholder" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <span class="tag">London</span>
            <h3>Borough Market</h3>
            <p>One of London’s most beloved food markets, famous for artisan stalls, fresh produce, street food, and a busy local atmosphere.</p>
            <p class="mini-note">Why we’re visiting: an easy first food stop with lots of options for everyone.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="place-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529655683826-aba9b3e77383?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Tower Bridge placeholder" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <span class="tag">London</span>
            <h3>Tower Bridge</h3>
            <p>A dramatic Victorian bridge and one of the most recognizable views in the city, perfect for classic London photos.</p>
            <p class="mini-note">Why we’re visiting: iconic skyline moment and family photo stop.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="place-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533929736458-ca588d08c8be?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Big Ben placeholder" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <span class="tag">London</span>
            <h3>Big Ben + Westminster</h3>
            <p>The heart of postcard London, known for Parliament, historic architecture, and the famous clock tower.</p>
            <p class="mini-note">Why we’re visiting: a must-see landmark that feels like London immediately.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="place-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504893524553-b855bce32c67?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Iceland landscape placeholder" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <span class="tag ice">Iceland</span>
            <h3>Geysir</h3>
            <p>A geothermal area known for erupting hot springs, steaming ground, and the strange, alive feeling of Iceland’s landscape.</p>
            <p class="mini-note">Why we’re visiting: one of the classic Golden Circle stops.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="place-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1476611338391-6f395a0ebc7b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Iceland waterfall placeholder" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <span class="tag ice">Iceland</span>
            <h3>Gullfoss Falls</h3>
            <p>A powerful two-tier waterfall where glacial water drops into a deep canyon, often misty, loud, and unforgettable.</p>
            <p class="mini-note">Why we’re visiting: big waterfall energy and one of Iceland’s signature views.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="place-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Black sand beach placeholder" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <span class="tag ice">Iceland</span>
            <h3>Reynisfjara Beach</h3>
            <p>A black sand beach famous for basalt columns, sea stacks, dramatic waves, and a moody volcanic coastline.</p>
            <p class="mini-note">Why we’re visiting: cinematic scenery and a completely different kind of beach.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="stays">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>Where We’re Staying</h2>
        <p>This page can hold hotel photos, campsite notes, check-in details, parking, nearby food, and anything the family needs to know.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stays-grid">
        <article class="stay-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="Hotel placeholder" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <span class="tag stay">London Stay</span>
            <h3>Hyatt Regency London Blackfriars</h3>
            <p>Our London home base from June 3 to June 6. Convenient for sightseeing, transit, food, and getting around central London.</p>
            <p class="mini-note">Add later: address, confirmation number, check-in time, breakfast notes, and nearby stations.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="stay-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517824806704-9040b037703b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" alt="Campervan placeholder" />
          <div class="card-body">
            <span class="tag stay">Iceland Stay</span>
            <h3>Campervan + Campsites</h3>
            <p>Our Iceland setup from June 6 to June 13. This card can turn into a full campsite list with nightly locations and facilities.</p>
            <p class="mini-note">Add later: rental company, pickup time, campsite names, showers, laundry, and backup stays.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <strong>London & Iceland · June 2026</strong>
    <p>Built as a living guidebook. Add details as the trip becomes real.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
